<FictionLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <p>uhhhhhhh WIP.... but like... sometimes i write or draw stuff?? sometimes it's about these dumb nerds who i made up and am obsessed with???</p>
    <p>for now you might be interested to check out my <a href="https://toyhou.se/caesium" rel="noopener noreferrer">toyhouse</a> or <a href="https://archiveofourown.org/users/entropically" rel="noopener noreferrer">ao3</a>? or even my silly little twitter project called <a href="https://twitter.com/dailytrashkid" rel="noopener noreferrer">the daily trashkid</a> where for a little while i tried to tweet a random fact about one of my characters every day.</p>
    <p>i honestly don't even have that many different characters anymore (and i tend to reuse the same few in different stories) but, as for the ones i do have, i love them dearly.... actually i've been mainly focused on the same like 3 of them for about 15 years now, despite not having any specific project i use them in, lmao.</p>
