    <h2>projects/settings</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <details>
                <summary><a href="https://caesiumtea.gitlab.io/symposiac-landing/">symposiac</a></summary>
                <p>one of my very rare attempts at a "real" "novel". except that it's actually fanfic for the TTRPG <a href="https://massifpress.com/lancer" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lancer</a>--or more specifically, it's the backstory of the lancer character that i created and then never got a chance to play.</p>
                <p>when an NHP researcher disappears overnight, his experimental subject goes rogue and recruits a fellow scientist to track down his whereabouts. in their pursuit, the pair become the unlikely co-pilots of the mech suit ophanim, scouring the galaxy for clues while hunting bounties as their cover.</p>
                <p>read the <a href="https://archiveofourown.org/works/25852267" rel="noopener noreferrer">fic that started it all</a> on ao3.</p>
            </details>
        </li>
        <li>
